track_notes: This track shows my route for a two-summit day, starting with 80 Mountain and then on to Gomez Peak.  There are trails the entire way, somewhat rocky but really quite nice.  Views from the top are excellent and there are shrubs and trees to attach a mast.  Gomez Peak is more popular, when I was there on a Saturday afternoon there were numerous other visitors.
